        -- But we need to show X = sSup (B N₁ hN₁)
        -- This is true because X = N₁ and N₁ is a single submodule
        -- Wait, X = sSup (B N₀ hN₀) = N₀
        -- And N₁ = X
        -- So N₁ is N₀
        -- This is getting confusing
